data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the highly sought-after Deer Creek School District! This stunning 3-bedroom residence, complete with a study or optional 4th bedroom, sits on half an acre of land. With modern upgrades including a new pump for the aerobic septic tank and a tankless water heater installed less than a year ago, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style.
